name: 賢い鳥と彼の生徒 / KASHIKOI TORI TO KARE NO SEITO
description: The wise bird and his student. Both Yōkai creatures. One is a magical bird that can turn invisible, but speaks into the ear of its apprentice bird-human sorcerer. The magic bird is the wise one and advises and instructs his student on aspects of sorcery and the occult arts. Weird Japanese Toys, 2021.
